CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 6, 1952, pg. 2, reads: "5,000 Negroes Used Highland Park Pool This Year - Pool Officials - Head life guard Harry Love and pool superintendent Richard (Bob) Kelleher played leading roles in smooth operation at Highland Park Pool this summer. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Lifeguard Harry Love wearing bathing suit, and Richard "Bob" Kelleher seated on bench at Highland Park swimming pool
